verbose_text: Intriguingly, post-treatment levels of both IFN-alpha2 and BAFF were higher in ANA positive, than ANA negative patients among ADA positive group (XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY), and IFN-alpha2 showed weak positive correlation with ADA (r = 0.314, p = 0.019) and ANA (r = 0.338, p = 0.012).
evidence: levels of both IFN-alpha2 and BAFF
